msgid "Zamonaviy veterinariya klinikasi"
msgstr "Modern veterinary clinic"

msgid "Hayvoningiz sog‘lig‘i biz uchun muhim"
msgstr "Your pet’s health matters to us"

msgid "VetClinic — hayvonlar sog‘lig‘i uchun zamonaviy veterinariya xizmatlarini taqdim etuvchi klinika. Arizalar Telegram bot orqali qabul qilinadi va mutaxassislarimiz siz bilan bog‘lanadi."
msgstr "VetClinic is a clinic providing modern veterinary services for animal health. Applications are accepted through the Telegram bot, and our specialists will contact you."

msgid "Xizmatlarni ko‘rish"
msgstr "View services"

msgid "Bemor hayvonlar"
msgstr "Animal patients"

msgid "Mutaxassislar"
msgstr "Specialists"

msgid "Mamnun mijozlar"
msgstr "Satisfied clients"

msgid "Ariza yuborish qanday ishlaydi?"
msgstr "How does application submission work?"

msgid "Oddiy va qulay jarayon"
msgstr "A simple and convenient process"

msgid "Telegram botga o‘ting va kerakli ma’lumotlarni yuboring"
msgstr "Go to the Telegram bot and send the required information"

msgid "Klinika xodimlari arizangizni ko‘rib chiqadi"
msgstr "Clinic staff will review your application"

msgid "Siz bilan bog‘lanib, qulay vaqt kelishiladi"
msgstr "You will be contacted to agree on a convenient time"

msgid "Hayvoningiz klinikada ko‘rikdan o‘tkaziladi"
msgstr "Your pet will be examined at the clinic"

msgid "Klinikamiz xizmatlari"
msgstr "Our clinic services"

msgid "Hayvonlar salomatligi uchun zarur bo‘lgan asosiy veterinariya, laboratoriya va diagnostika xizmatlari."
msgstr "Core veterinary, laboratory, and diagnostic services needed for animal health."

msgid "Hayvonning umumiy holati tekshiriladi va davolash yo‘nalishi belgilanadi."
msgstr "The animal’s general condition is checked and the treatment direction is determined."

msgid "Tahlil so‘rovlari laboratoriya xodimlari tomonidan qayta ishlanadi."
msgstr "Analysis requests are processed by laboratory staff."

msgid "Natijalar asosida diagnostik xulosa va tavsiyalar tayyorlanadi."
msgstr "Diagnostic conclusions and recommendations are prepared based on results."

msgid "Barcha xizmatlarni ko‘rish"
msgstr "View all services"

msgid "Afzalliklar"
msgstr "Advantages"

msgid "Nega VetClinic’ni tanlashadi?"
msgstr "Why choose VetClinic?"

msgid "VetClinic hayvonlar salomatligiga mas’uliyat bilan yondashadi. Biz mijozlarga qulay, tezkor va ishonchli veterinariya xizmatlarini taqdim etishga harakat qilamiz."
msgstr "VetClinic takes animal health seriously. We strive to provide convenient, fast, and reliable veterinary services."

msgid "Tajribali veterinarlar hayvoningiz holatini diqqat bilan tekshiradi."
msgstr "Experienced veterinarians carefully examine your pet’s condition."

msgid "Laboratoriya tahlillari va diagnostika xizmatlari mavjud."
msgstr "Laboratory tests and diagnostic services are available."

msgid "Har bir hayvonga mehr va individual yondashuv asosida xizmat ko‘rsatiladi."
msgstr "Every animal receives caring and individual attention."

msgid "Bizning afzalliklarimiz"
msgstr "Our advantages"

msgid "Qulay murojaat"
msgstr "Convenient application"

msgid "Telegram bot orqali tez va oson ariza yuborish mumkin."
msgstr "You can quickly and easily submit an application through the Telegram bot."

msgid "Malakali mutaxassislar"
msgstr "Qualified specialists"

msgid "Hayvonlar salomatligi bo‘yicha tajribali xodimlar xizmat ko‘rsatadi."
msgstr "Experienced animal health staff provide services."

msgid "Zamonaviy yondashuv"
msgstr "Modern approach"

msgid "Ko‘rik, tahlil va diagnostika jarayonlari tartibli olib boriladi."
msgstr "Examination, analysis, and diagnostic processes are managed in an organized way."

msgid "Ishonchli xizmat"
msgstr "Reliable service"

msgid "Mijozlarga tushunarli, qulay va sifatli xizmat ko‘rsatish maqsad qilingan."
msgstr "Our goal is to provide clear, convenient, and quality service to clients."

msgid "Foydali ma’lumotlar"
msgstr "Useful information"

msgid "Hayvonlar parvarishi, emlash, profilaktika va klinika yangiliklari haqida."
msgstr "About animal care, vaccination, prevention, and clinic news."

msgid "Laboratoriya tahlillari nima uchun kerak?"
msgstr "Why are laboratory tests needed?"

msgid "Tahlillar kasallikni aniqlash va davolash yo‘nalishini tanlashda yordam beradi."
msgstr "Tests help identify diseases and choose a treatment direction."

msgid "Hayvonlarni vaqtida emlash muhim"
msgstr "Timely vaccination of animals is important"

msgid "Profilaktik emlashlar ko‘plab xavfli kasalliklarning oldini oladi."
msgstr "Preventive vaccinations help prevent many dangerous diseases."

msgid "Uy hayvonlarini parvarish qilish"
msgstr "Pet care"

msgid "To‘g‘ri ovqatlantirish va muntazam ko‘rik sog‘liqni saqlashga yordam beradi."
msgstr "Proper feeding and regular checkups help maintain health."

msgid "Yangiliklarni ko‘rish"
msgstr "View news"

msgid "Ariza yuborish uchun Telegram botga o‘ting. Klinikamiz xodimlari arizangizni ko‘rib chiqib, siz bilan bog‘lanadi."
msgstr "To submit an application, go to the Telegram bot. Our clinic staff will review it and contact you."

msgid "Telegram botga o‘tish"
msgstr "Go to Telegram bot"
